metadata.name: Sensual Artifact Part 1
metadata.description:
Feelings are a powerful driving force.

We experience a huge range of emotions, triggered by feelings over which we have no control.

It's what defines us, what we follow.

Each painting in this collection reflects exactly how you feel, what you want to see in it.

Feel the attraction and master the sensual artifact that evoked it.

4000x4000 px
